Package: pistomp-recovery
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3, jack2-pistomp,
 lg-pistomp, libasound2, libfreetype6
Description: Package update and recovery service for pi-Stomp
 Recovery service that provides LCD-based factory reset, package rollback,
 and OTA update management. Runs as a systemd service triggered on
 mod-ala-pi-stomp failure (3 crashes in 3 minutes).
